Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.17,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:08.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:10.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano, let's have a drink after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:12.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:14.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you drank too much last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:16.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that the only reason for me to turn down your invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:18.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You seemed pretty busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:21.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If you need any help, just say the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:21.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can still make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:23.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That means that Nakano haven't fully trusted you just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's not true. Lately the way that she calls my name is filled with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She always say your name with the same tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 3 is also peaceful today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about you, Saruwatari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:34.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She looks at me with respect. Ask me anything about horse racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:37.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai from Department 1 is amazing, I heard that he got another project.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:39.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's the next ace for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:42.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you hear about it? It seems like our company has begun restructuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:43.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:45.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The overseas sales department was dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard that the event department will also be abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:49.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I guess the department with the worst sales is on the chopping block.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, our department should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:53.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, Department 3 is in a pinch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:54.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If things keep up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:01.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:04.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I just have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:09.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:13.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I had no idea that Nakano-san, whom I met at a bar, was from an event company.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that you were just hitting on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:18.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm here to talk business.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Home medical equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:23.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're still a new start-up company
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:29.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,but we want to set up a big booth at the upcoming Mirai Expo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:31.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That Mirai Expo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:33.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The one at Makuhari?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:33.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:37.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it attracts a lot of attention from the media, we would like to show off our products there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, we don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it too hard to pull off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:48.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A chance to comeback from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:53.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:58.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Overtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:03.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san, it's the most pointless time in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I take back what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai, don't bother Nakano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not bothering her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you working on? A new proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Inuzuka-san, don't bother her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I only asked her a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:20.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:21.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want the booth to look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is white the main color?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, it's simple, but I want it to look stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want this monitor to display a video promoting the products.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Something that packs a punch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want it to stand out from the other booths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think about the content ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:41.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,About the Mirai Expo booth space,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have secured the desired spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:48.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we're a little over budget on the booth decorations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:50.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,but I'll try to keep it within the total budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, I'll have it before the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:59.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, the estimation is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,3 minutes has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:12.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:15.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:16.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have bags under your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:17.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you get 8 hours of sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I never slept for that long to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How do I put it, you're unusual, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:27.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:30.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can finish your work on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:32.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that you can work even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:35.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're asking why am I in the laid back Department 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Our department is comfortable, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,People can tell if you're capable or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:43.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of thing that builds trust with the client!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We don't have to always run as fast as possible in life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If jogging is comfortable, then so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:50.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, I have to do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:01.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We couldn't get funding from investors as much as we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:03.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What happens with Mirai Expo then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All the budget that we hoped for is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We have booked the space and have begun the production.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to cancel everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy to cancel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:14.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're just a start-up company after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:19.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A start-up company...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's all, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:25.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:36.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're going to give this to Chiemi-chan for her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's to celebrate her 20th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that this is too heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want her to question my taste by giving her common bath products.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Bath products is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:48.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're impartial.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:51.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:54.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Which one do you think is better, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Either one is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:58.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Either one is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Chiemi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:03.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This one is a big no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Which one should I pick then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Either one is fine! Think about it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:09.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:14.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:30.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where is Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She told me this morning that she's going to take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:33.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Taking the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Maybe she has a bad hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is the first time that Nakano is taking some time off since she came to Department 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She wasn't part of Department 3 since the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, she was reassigned here just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:50.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The department that she was originally assigned to is called the newbie destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All the seniors around her was cold to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,they didn't teach her anything about her job at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:12.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And them, Chief Inuzuka found her crying in the smoking area,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and asked her to join his department, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I just can't leave a crying kitten alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:20.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Her style of not relying on others, started from way back then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,My opinion of Nakano-san has changed 180 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How did you see Nakano-san before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even though she's like that, she loves this department.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,20 million in damages is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do I have to take responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Or change jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Do you want me to bring you Pocari and jelly?]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[Did something happened?]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[No.]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:16.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,[If you're fine, then let's have dinner.]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard that you wanted me to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think the three of us hanging out together is great?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:40.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why did you took the day off all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's see, because I felt like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I admire that strong will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Saruwatari-san, can you prepare the materials for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:48.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm in that kind of mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:55.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please say something will you? Like "Are you an idiot?".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:57.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:09.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please rely on me more will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:13.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you thought I was quite crazy at first, but
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:18.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've made improvements after improvements and now I've become a capable person...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji-kun is like this after just 2 rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:23.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's like this after an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He gets drunk according to the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's new, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:30.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go to another place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is this THE plastic model shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is the oasis that I found in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is also my love nest with Chiemi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll have to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:41.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You've come all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in plastic models at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone says that at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Pardon our intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:53.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is she your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm her colleague, Nakano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:10:00.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I heard stories about you from Zakunee, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Chiemi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I also heard stories about you from Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not another word, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is this your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,First time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:10.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is your first time building a plastic model, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I said that I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you like? Gundam? Evangelion? Love Live!? Ultraman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I loved Ultraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean that I want to build one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's already searching for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:25.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ultraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:32.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's different from the Ultraman that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks modern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:40.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This Ultraman is set several decades after the well-known {\i1}tokusatsu{\i0} series Ultraman produced by Tsuburaya Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It doesn't connect to the larger Ultraman series, just like Ultraseven.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:46.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The comic takes place in an alternate universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:54.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The most defining feature of this series is the Ultraman is not an alien, but a human wearing a reinforced suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? He doesn't get bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,On top of that, that person is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,a troubled high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:05.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A troubled high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's actually so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:09.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try building it, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:09.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:10.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is your hobby, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the hobby of everyone in Deparment 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Preparation is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I may not look like it, but I'm actually clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware, I sit right next to you everyday after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I may put the arms and legs backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's why we're going to build this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:31.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that even allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can do anything with plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:38.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here we go, ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Open the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:45.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I take it all out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's more detailed than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:54.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, let's do that at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're also painting the runners today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is possible because each runner are different colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko, you never showed that look before at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:26.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You paint red for the red parts, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Red for the red parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You use silver for the silver parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:36.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's all dried up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please build the torso, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll build the legs and Shinji will build the arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your way of doing things is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She has become a proper senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You look so happy, Yassan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.74,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where should I start cutting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,G7.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:59.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,G7.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Number 7 is this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please cut it from the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:06.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,From the bottom? \N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you going to cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter where I cut it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, you were going to cut it's waist, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:31.23,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Waist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? How much of all of these is the waist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, you're getting attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san, don't panic and just take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:48.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did I made a mistake? \N-Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:56.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please cut the part where it still has the remains of the gate one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's called second cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Second cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:00.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where is the B runner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:01.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:02.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:13.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:16.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't force it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:33.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please do it more gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:39.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:55.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:00.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What a nice sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:27.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It has a wide range of motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't put it in at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's no good if you force it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't put it in at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:43.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Flexibility and strength are the essence of building plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:53.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:14.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Evertything good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks like a real joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:34.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because there are ball joints inside the chest and waist,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:38.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,that allows the figure to have a wide range of motion and so you can make it do all kinds of poses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Ultraman looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:49.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's with you all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:53.85,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if it's crying, laughing or angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it's kinda sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:59.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He is a lone warrior who does not show any expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:02.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little too much of an act of selfless love to protect the earth by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I would want to be adored by all human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is the fate of a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:09.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that it's easier to do anything with others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't handle being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:18.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please proceed, Riko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:10.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's your job to assemble it, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:18.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's decide the pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:47.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:28.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ultraman, give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Give birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is how we do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The Specium Beam is so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The way the knees bend, it's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:38.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the magic of range of motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the magic of range of motion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The plastic model road is so deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:46.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,They built most of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:13.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to go to the plastic model shop with Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She's more clumsy that I expected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,She would have broke it if we let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:18.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:20.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:23.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:27.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You took way too long to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about me, Nakano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:00.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:06.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,WHAT??
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is beyond my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano-san, what do you think about this proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.14,0:21:19.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? Manten Nodoame Mirai Expo event?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I remembered that their President is interested in doing something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:25.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about changing the decoration of the booth to match Manten Nodoame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Chief, I managed to secure an appointment with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:29.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Appointment? We're doing to do the presentation right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:33.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It seems like you're relying on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:34.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:50.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nakano is apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:58.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I kept it all by myself and caused trouble to Department 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:02.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You really haven't changed, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.90,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't be a stranger, Nakano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:07.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, speed is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:09.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go do the presentation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:10.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:15.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Nakano.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:16.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:28.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:30.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,